import React from 'react';
import { Container, Row, Col, Card, ListGroup, Button } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { FaCodeBranch, FaStar, FaEye, FaExclamationCircle } from 'react-icons/fa'; // Import icons
import './Dashboard.css'; // Create a CSS file for custom styling

function Dashboard() {
  return (
    <Container fluid className="dashboard-container">
      <Row>
        <Col md={3} className="sidebar">
          <Card>
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Repositories</Card.Title>
              <ListGroup variant="flush">
                <ListGroup.Item>MyProject</ListGroup.Item>
                <ListGroup.Item>AnotherRepo</ListGroup.Item>
                {/* Add more repositories */}
              </ListGroup>
            </Card.Body>
          </Card>
        </Col>
        <Col md={9} className="main-content">
          <Row>
            <Col md={6}>
              <Card>
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>Recent Activity</Card.Title>
                  <ListGroup variant="flush">
                    <ListGroup.Item>
                      <FaCodeBranch /> Updated branch 'main'
                    </ListGroup.Item>
                    <ListGroup.Item>
                      <FaStar /> Starred repository 'AwesomeLib'
                    </ListGroup.Item>
                    {/* Add more activity items */}
                  </ListGroup>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>
            <Col md={6}>
              <Card>
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>Issues</Card.Title>
                  <ListGroup variant="flush">
                    <ListGroup.Item>
                      <FaExclamationCircle /> Issue #12: Bug fix needed
                    </ListGroup.Item>
                    <ListGroup.Item>
                      <FaExclamationCircle /> Issue #15: Feature request
                    </ListGroup.Item>
                    {/* Add more issues */}
                  </ListGroup>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row className="mt-4">
            <Col>
              <Card>
                <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>Popular Repositories</Card.Title>
                  <ListGroup variant="flush">
                    <ListGroup.Item>
                      <FaEye /> Project A (100 views)
                    </ListGroup.Item>
                    <ListGroup.Item>
                      <FaStar /> Project B (50 stars)
                    </ListGroup.Item>
                    {/* Add more popular repositories */}
                  </ListGroup>
                </Card.Body>
              </Card>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default Dashboard;
